<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.4.8">
<l>tiruvuṭai maṉṉaraik kāṇi ṟirumālaik kaṇṭēṉē yeṉṉu</l>
<l>muruvuṭai vaṇṇaṅkaḷ kāṇi lulakaḷan tā ṉeṉṟu tuḷḷuṅ</l>
<l>karuvuṭait tēvilka ḷellāṅ kaṭalvaṇṇaṉ kōyilē yeṉṉum</l>
<l>veruvilum vīḻvilu mōvāḷ kaṇṇaṉ kaḻalkaḷ virumpumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When she sees resplendent kings she says “I have seen Tirumāl”,</l>
<l>if she sees beautiful colours she leaps, saying “he has measured the world”,</l>
<l>all the houses of shrine-possessing gods she calls “temples to him of ocean colour”,</l>
<l>Whether she is frightended or falls she won’t leave off the desire for the anklets of Kaṇṇaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
